   "html": "\n[ まつい・いわね ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n中支那方面軍司令官兼上海派遣軍司令官、ハルピン特務機関長、陸軍大将、Ａ級戦犯"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "hidden"
   },
   "html": "<a name=\"s1\"></a>\n<a href=\"#s1\">＝</a><a href=\"#h\">△</a><a href=\"#h\">◎</a><a href=\"#s2\">▽</a><a href=\"#s1\">＝</a>"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　愛知県出身。陸士卒。陸大卒。陸大在学中に日露戦争に従軍。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　その後、中国に駐在中は、国民党の<a href=\"../p/enseigai.html\">袁世凱</a>打倒に協力。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　いったんは予備役に編入されるも、日中戦争が起こり現役に復帰。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　上海派遣軍司令官、次いで中支那方面軍司令官に就任、首都南京を攻略し復員。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　戦後、Ａ級戦犯として<a href=\"../1937/12gyaku.html\">南京大虐殺</a>の責任を問われ、<a href=\"../1948/11tokyo.html\">東京裁判で「絞首刑」の判決</a>。<a href=\"../1948/12senpa.html\">刑死</a>。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
